Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.24,0:23:17.74,jpA.sub,NTP,0,0,0,,回せ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.39,0:23:24.31,JP.SONG,NTP,0,0,0,,希望照らす光の歌を
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.79,0:23:19.06,jpA.sub,NTP,0,0,0,,回してください
